    "description": {
      "value": "<p>&gt;<a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sfrpg.class-features\" data-id=\"hIhgdXnqGHBm0A64\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Envoy Improvisation</a></p>\n        <p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl21_LabelName\">As a standard action, you can encourage a single ally within 60 feet to focus on the danger at hand. If that ally is @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.MZ8OoH1GE9qDMyCD]{Flat-Footed} or off-target, you end that condition. If circumstances would cause the ally to immediately become @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.MZ8OoH1GE9qDMyCD]{Flat-Footed} or off-target again, you instead suppress that condition for 1 round.</span></p>",
